This function returns the current z position of the given audio emitter.
The index of the emitter to use.

{ANY_CODE} if audio_emitter_get_z(emitter_player) != 0
{nbsp_x3}{
{nbsp_x3}var ex = audio_emitter_get_x(emitter_player);
{nbsp_x3}var ey = audio_emitter_get_y(emitter_player);
{nbsp_x3}audio_emitter_position(emitter_player, ex, ey, 0);
{nbsp_x3}}
The above code checks the current z position of a given emitter and if it is not equal to 0, it is set to 0.
